# Sibling monorepo packages that Vercel shouldn't upload or type-check.
# apps/companion is the Tauri desktop companion — built separately with
# its own toolchain. Its TypeScript imports (e.g. @tauri-apps/api/core)
# aren't in the web app's dependency tree, so leaving apps/ in the Vercel
# upload causes the Next.js production build to fail with
#   "Cannot find module '@tauri-apps/api/core'"
# even though tsconfig.json already excludes the directory.
apps
